Package com.eclipsesource.tabris.app

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    App
    The App client service represents the App that is calling the Tabris server.
    AppListener
    An AppListener will be called when an AppEvent was fired within the App.
    BackNavigationListener
    A BackNavigationListener is registered using App.addBackNavigationListener(BackNavigationListener) and will be notified when the user presses the back button if available on the device.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AppEvent
    The AppEvent represents an event instance of a specific EventType.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    EventType
    The EventType is used to specify different types of events.
